         <h1 align="center">Biology Internship Application</h1>
         <h4 align="center">Submit a typed, completed, and signed form with an
            attached, printed copy of your unofficial academic transcript
            (obtained from Banner) to the SST Office in the Allied Health
            and Sciences (H2) Building, Room 3209.<br><br>
            <strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> The information you submit will be used to determine if
            you will be accepted to participate in the Program. Completion of this application does NOT
            guarantee your acceptance into the Biology Internship Program and/or enrollment in BIOL4800.
            <br><br>
            Please remember to upload all required application materials (transcript, essay,
            preceptor form if picking your own site, and other necessary documents) as a part
            of your application.
         </h4>
